# Push Changes to GitHub

After making any edits to this project, always push the changes to:

**https://github.com/BethelHills/email-template-replication-trial-2.git**

Workflow:
1. Stage changes: `git add .`
2. Commit with a descriptive message: `git commit -m "..."`
3. Push: `git push origin main`
